OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1773864689
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough in with chance to become
OL,4,CCity of Culture 2029
OL,6,FThe chance for Middlesbrough to become
OL,7,FUK City of Culture 2029 has been
OL,8,Fdescribed by its mayor as a "once in a
OL,9,Fgeneration opportunity".
OL,11,FThe town is one of four locations
OL,12,Fwithout city status to make the long-
OL,13,Flist for the City of Culture title
OL,14,Fwhich will come for the first time
OL,15,Fwith a #10million cash reward.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
