SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1773864689
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough in with chance to become
OL,4,CCity of Culture 2029
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough is joined by Inverness-
OL,7,FHighland, Ipswich, Milton Keynes,
OL,8,FPortsmouth, Swindon, Sheffield,
OL,9,FBlackpool and Wrexham hoping to follow
OL,10,FBradford which was given the title in
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,FWelcoming the news, Middlesbrough
OL,14,FMayor Chris Cooke said: "Our bid takes
OL,15,FMiddlesbrough's motto, 'Erimus', -
OL,16,Fwhich translates to 'We Shall Be' -
OL,17,Fliterally.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1773864689
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough in with chance to become
OL,4,CCity of Culture 2029
OL,6,F"It brings together our history as an
OL,7,Findustrial powerhouse with our
OL,8,Fambition to become the UK's most
OL,9,Fcreative place.
OL,11,F"I am delighted that we've been
OL,12,Flonglisted for what would be a once in
OL,13,Fa generation opportunity to celebrate
OL,14,Fthe creativity of our residents,
OL,15,Fartists and businesses and change how
OL,16,Fpeople view Middlesbrough."
OL,18,FThe Department for Culture, Media and
OL,19,FSport said the nine contenders will
OL,20,Feach receive #60,000 to develop full
OL,21,Fbids.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
