OL,3,CMiddlesbrough in with chance to become
OL,4,CCity of Culture 2029
OL,6,FThe winner will then receive
OL,7,F#10million to deliver a year of
OL,8,Fcultural activities, with three others
OL,9,Fcollecting #125,000 for elements of
OL,10,Ftheir bid.
OL,12,FThe City of Culture programme would be
OL,13,Fled by Middlesbrough Council, Teesside
OL,14,FUniversity and the Middlesbrough
OL,15,FCultural Partnership.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
