CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1773864689
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough in with chance to become
OL,4,CCity of Culture 2029
OL,6,FHe said the competition used culture
OL,7,Fas a 'creative catalyst for change,
OL,8,Fraising awareness and changing
OL,9,Fperceptions'.
OL,11,F"Derry-Londonderry, Hull, Coventry
OL,12,Fand, more recently, Bradford, have all
OL,13,Fdemonstrated the quality and depth of
OL,14,Fcultural activity embedded across the
OL,15,FUK, as well as the benefits of simply
OL,16,Ftaking part," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
