PN,42207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1773864689
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough in with chance to become
OL,4,CCity of Culture 2029
OL,6,F"The competition brings people
OL,7,Ftogether, to talk to each other rather
OL,8,Fthan at each other, sharing
OL,9,Fcommonality and tolerating difference.
OL,10,FAbove all, allowing places to
OL,11,Fdemonstrate their own pride in their
OL,12,Fplaces."
OL,14,FThe previous winner, Bradford, hosted
OL,15,F5,000 events over the year, attracting
OL,16,Fthree million people.
OL,18,FThe UK City of Culture 2029 winner
OL,19,Fwill be announced later this year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
